qMeasure.qDef:
rangemin(1, 
    pick(match(v_ViewUptake & '_' & v_ViewTargetGroup, 'FIRST_80', 'SECOND_80', 'FIRST_HCW', 'SECOND_HCW', 'FIRST_LTCF', 'SECOND_LTCF'),
      sum({<[Member State]=>}Uptake1st_80),
      sum({<[Member State]=>}Uptake2nd_80),
      sum({<[Member State]=>} Uptake1st_HCW),
      sum({<[Member State]=>} Uptake2nd_HCW),
      sum({<[Member State]=>} Uptake1st_LTCF),
      sum({<[Member State]=>} Uptake2nd_LTCF)
    )
)
qMeasure.qLabelExpression:
=pick(match(v_ViewUptake & '_' & v_ViewTargetGroup , 'FIRST_80', 'SECOND_80', 'FIRST_HCW', 'SECOND_HCW', 'FIRST_LTCF', 'SECOND_LTCF'),
'Uptake at least one dose (%) - 80 years old and above',
'Uptake full vaccination (%) - 80 years old and above',
'Uptake at least one dose (%) - Healthcare Workers',
'Uptake full vaccination (%) - Healthcare Workers',
'Uptake at least one dose (%) - LTCF residents',
'Uptake full vaccination (%) - LTCF residents',
)
